[0.172, "o", "\r\nв•”в•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•—\r\nв•‘     Halo AI Core вЂ” Install Done      в•‘\r\nв•љв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ќ\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \"There is no spoon.\" вЂ” The Matrix\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  в”Ђв”Ђ EVERYTHING RUNS THROUGH LEMOND в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Lemonade (web UI + all APIs):\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    http://localhost:13305\r\n    SSH: ssh -L 13305:localhost:13305 strixhalo\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Built-in router on :13305 serves:\r\n    OpenAI API:    /v1/chat/completions\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Anthropic API: /v1/messages\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Ollama API:    /api/chat\r\n    Web UI:        / (browser)\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Claude Code (local AI coding agent):\r\n    lemonade launch claude -m <model-name>\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n  Dashboard:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    http://localhost:80\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  в”Ђв”Ђ IMPORTANT в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Reboot your machine to start all services:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    sudo reboot\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Services are enabled and will start automatically on boot.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  They will NOT run until you reboot.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  в”Ђв”Ђ NEXT STEPS (after reboot) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  1. Open http://localhost:13305 вЂ” load a model, start chatting\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  2. Launch Claude Code with local models:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "     lemonade launch claude -m <model-name>\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  3. Check status:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "     ./install.sh --status\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[0;32mвњ“\u001b[0m Installation complete.\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  \u001b[0;32mвњ“\u001b[0m Full log: /home/bcloud/.local/log/halo-ai-core-install.log\r\n"]
